messages.message:
Great! For multer, you need to set limits in your multer configuration. Here's what you need to do:

```javascript
const upload = multer({
  dest: 'uploads/',
  limits: {
    fileSize: 10 * 1024 * 1024 // 10MB in bytes
  }
});
```

Also make sure your express.json() middleware has matching limits:

```javascript
app.use(express.json({limit: '10mb'}));
app.use(express.urlencoded({limit: '10mb', extended: true}));
```
